asses have a null write method. I'll need to verify that cloning requires a public no-arg constructor and proper setters, so adding some assertions is a good idea.\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0602a48bffbeae510169f965be220081969cecd1b85c8cb9e1\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp-WXJj2nNaypsqLnXBTnUo_iXnWyUS3HYyWOIxELSmSNVEicbBAFjCO63wnmzfv71Mk__73DVHCOaMM8DdLPlJPbR_HZbK_4xf2Xr_Y_HckVbGT70UwYcrJACBNUJfv3CE8Na2AAby96GXAE3yswqeikdyDqjs4G6pthnQjzuzO9GLKkdmeKyK_ArB16I8f2UZzeCIMDuukBhS9Z0XUjtgETmVNsZv9dadrYrrel0PnhfkyKmtrgWDy4PLmF3gHYBm7HW3H7Xr9tb01E4z7YTjJkXEUTbKcOgsX4KxnDGgSJ90YjHSC0dPx76FSv6cg1lsziqGO80wwITJ40DPa_jbXzhwMWvzIOHwpDBfSQtNxbwpQncm9jU425O-fpb7foMmXY_lfo4WR9d7OJlkBBLXNSbjnMfJao86YS9ASBQ5nKC5WVLrXvhcB5Bi-sI1O7GrBGPNV13RSjm0Zqc1AJWgAsBayeyujT7axPzyrzeHh-onqMzAhHPp83hXQRSMEs4RFo9XUYoWc1xUd-f5OXwPMRQ0qXqhM430AXvYPvLQPHYZmk9IFTdGU5a24h51jMht0wnjO2HGSeH0oEhkkFbmNC437JtXPgVb-Ew6LRADZRcKYMqVWjf32g0UVdVQxpNodr7d5XT8rVS3vfwh74_2pkhnLhxYTVTOKYUwYTiGddYLpsmBjMWyVEH3Msq_PVsRvrlWFR7u3PLHDJJed4HQ1QIn9jIvtDmRcBdDuSj4uLURl9oS8rJV--tG-bF2O-WYURP3zgfwZu0M9CQqJ52OT_UWbHlCl1rOSxKfz0gL-U8A1ebUgrXXQ1mUK-keitSIuQpA_yjK5YoBjhbzOT0y1yHyOZZsI4MqsAe-BqAGLTxF83LspuILJCDzCtAb74SRo7bLBRE1d4PMTTEv4KreLAqRmVsMq0KRpnML00xyPIwQLaNKjzJhOaGkosEtdmFFD3B-4qjVpKny8ET3QXP9irn0yKJi_Vkw8vMSgUC7iQke0R7f0vREX2dDt9AjImJKZK17-jaSKt28bxh_nXMJ_ivmdRs-fve1Xil44I5DR4CoAhLD6fXBRYF7xBQDY36kLIzxL8HBYF66ux-_UWlz3KVCxS9_K9U6KkiedTV9CztHOGSRqbnoDK9V80X3Yc1_Xehh0-VCkCL030etQxU6nS6OAtuBbpQ4DbUWUoOVQEsNIKjhsVpBPAwSg5tYqW0odCRzeYqeoa9G7smeAU573E5tZsNPNlFV1lnHVLVXpZJl9bqCJLXsJYVAqtoWcWPC3Rh22IpzbX0otkPILkijxuhf2tBe_i3z24EhYfywodhj4s3PDk3Ns9rmPl4D4_tmn0XyTFWQBK8V2FrFbNP3F-RslNX2KZ5nJpjq45bllXWAGBydhOs_8A1wTESpap-fOWnNJTSjL4atSBN5KtJ-Al474wfJlHqiJLEfq4e2eIJcQq59C5hYMPh9BhZrDGaS7-9aWFnmsPE72FBy6VwIECRW32oh2K6A97c31EVOVGukn0fa7Wo2Piqd3mt3xnbcsXtvRIzDwvhP94DplVf_jnEX6Vg6PkmxwidqIOsl0C3KNWa6UoDLNJJB5mjyVYwyTTxI49A8IdBGNKnz6kaVJCjVrM45bGMWj-a1d4ZTLS8iBcdFUfMDConqZXArqfD3